{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"73699549-7ac7-42e9-93e8-902daf08f74f","agentId":"ae5fb5542a2308d5e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"在 `/Users/admin/tianzi-rike/` 目录下，天子日课项目被另一个\"IT资产管理系统\"的文件污染了。git 工作区有 90 个变更。需要把两个项目拆开。\n\n## 操作步骤（严格按顺序执行）\n\n### 步骤 1：创建 IT 系统新目录并迁移文件\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p /Users/admin/it-asset-system\n\ncd /Users/admin/tianzi-rike\n\n# 把所有未跟踪的文件（??）移到 IT 系统目录，保持目录结构\ngit ls-files --others --exclude-standard | while read file; do\n  if [ -f \"$file\" ]; then\n    mkdir -p \"/Users/admin/it-asset-system/$(dirname \"$file\")\"\n    mv \"$file\" \"/Users/admin/it-asset-system/$file\"\n  fi\ndone\n```\n\n### 步骤 2：恢复被删除的天子日课文件\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/admin/tianzi-rike\ngit checkout HEAD -- app/habits/page.tsx app/insights/page.tsx app/review/page.tsx app/stats/page.tsx\ngit checkout HEAD -- lib/claude.ts lib/supabase.ts\ngit checkout HEAD -- app/api/habits/route.ts app/api/insights/route.ts app/api/logs/route.ts app/api/review/route.ts app/api/stats/route.ts app/api/profile/route.ts app/api/profile/input/route.ts\ngit checkout HEAD -- lib/store.ts lib/api.ts\n```\n\n### 步骤 3：恢复被 IT 系统篡改的非 miniapp 文件\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/admin/tianzi-rike\ngit checkout HEAD -- app/layout.tsx app/page.tsx app/globals.css app/profile/page.tsx\ngit checkout HEAD -- lib/prisma.ts prisma/schema.prisma\ngit checkout HEAD -- package.json package-lock.json\ngit checkout HEAD -- README.md .gitignore\ngit checkout HEAD -- components/layout/app-layout.tsx\n```\n\n### 步骤 4：清理残留的空目录\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/admin/tianzi-rike\n# 删除 IT 系统遗留的空目录\nfind app/api -name 'ai' -o -name 'approvals' -o -name 'assets' -o -name 'auth' -o -name 'it' -o -name 'test' -o -name 'tickets' | xargs rm -rf 2>/dev/null\nfind app -name 'apply' -o -name 'approvals' -o -name 'chat' -o -name 'dept-board' -o -name 'exec' -o -name 'home' -o -name 'it' -o -name 'login' -o -name 'my-assets' -o -name 'notifications' -o -name 'tickets' | xargs rm -rf 2>/dev/null\n# 删除 IT 系统的组件\nrm -rf components/asset-status-badge.tsx components/empty-state.tsx components/layout/header.tsx components/layout/sidebar.tsx components/notification-bell.tsx components/role-guard.tsx components/ticket-timeline.tsx components/ui/ 2>/dev/null\n```\n\n### 步骤 5：验证\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/admin/tianzi-rike\ngit status --short | head -30\n# 此时应该只剩下 miniapp/ 下的修改文件（M），不应该有 ?? 或 D 文件\n```\n\n### 步骤 6：确认 IT 系统文件已就位\n\n```bash\nls /Users/admin/it-asset-system/\n```\n\n完成后回报每一步的执行结果和最终 git status。"},"uuid":"7f986956-9557-4c7f-bd01-061aec9ce853","timestamp":"2026-05-11T09:26:28.114Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/Users/admin","sessionId":"c11efbf6-8e99-4d9b-9ae7-74981e78dedd","version":"2.1.133","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"adaptive-seeking-patterson"}
